{"tid":248293,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"恭喜晒！浪翠園樓價720萬元創97後新高","createTime":"2017-05-18T12:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T15:53:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ec70221987e2da0d014695010d3aa3ef3d8799","tid":248293,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:37:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170504/mobile/bkn-20170504181146408-0504_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170504%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170504181146408-0504_00842_001.html&d=07YJri3FF82qzkXABTRKfGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=291c2aaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170504/mobile/bkn-20170504181146408-0504_00842_001.html</a><br />\n2017年05月04日(四) 18:11   <br />\n<br />\n深井浪翠園屬少有樓價仍未突破97高峰的屋苑，但隨着大市向上，樓價亦逐漸逼近。市場消息稱，屋苑2期5座中層B室，實用面積802方呎，售價衝上720萬元，成交金額創97年底後新高，實用呎價8,978元。據了解，原業主持貨6年，單位升值約56.5%。"},{"pid":"84351a9c53317125ea36bf261108c5a87fe77028","tid":248293,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf522e724ed56e7e67073da130d3ade0138f49f1","tid":248293,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T15:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}